des: The Daily Challenge is designed to help you take ACTION in your business, health, or just life in general! Complete the Challenge to WIN the day! I challenge you to take ACTION today! The Daily Challenge will share one specific actionable item that can be accomplished during the day. It may challenging and push you outside of your comfort zone, but if you take action and stay focused on the task at hand you will rise VICTORIOUS everyday. Are you up to the CHALLENGE?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
